To build our app    -->   ./mvnw clean package -DskipTests
To build -->    docker build -t hotel-service:latest .
To run   -->    docker run -p 8081:8081 --network=host hotel-service:latest

To restart the docker
docker-compose down
docker-compose up --build


To go inside the container --> docker exec -it airbnb-poc-kafka-1 bash
To check topics creation --> kafka-topics --bootstrap-server localhost:9093 --list
To check how many messages ?  --> kafka-run-class kafka.tools.GetOffsetShell --broker-list localhost:9093 --topic hotel.updated --time -1


To run only infra -->  docker-compose up -d zookeeper kafka mysql redis elasticsearch kibana kafka-ui

To open redis --> docker exec -it $(docker ps --filter ancestor=redis:7 --format "{{.ID}}") redis-cli
